headline: Eastman Named as a 100 Best Corporate Citizen for 2025
summary: KINGSPORT, Tenn., September 16, 2025--Eastman (NYSE: EMN) has been recognized by 3BL, a leading sustainability communications partner, as one of the 100 Best Corporate Citizens of 2025.
